
Flags.
- flags are attached to types
- therefore types need to be generated asap (in Phase 1) before flags are interpreted (Phase 2)
- no flag =
    a) continue with the number of repetitions of previous occurrence of the type. But... An explicit 0 means this, so it would make no difference with 0
    b) keep adding, according to the last flag value
